OL,6,FHuw Edwards has resigned from the BBC
OL,7,F"on the basis of medical advice", the
OL,8,Fcorporation has said.
OL,10,FThe newsreader has been off air since
OL,11,FJuly last year claiming he had paid a
OL,12,Fyoung person for sexually explicit
OL,13,Fimages.
OL,15,FA statement from a BBC spokesperson
OL,16,Fsaid: "Huw Edwards has today resigned
OL,17,Fand left the BBC.
