OL,6,FIn a letter to BBC News, the young
OL,7,Fperson at the centre of the Edwards
OL,8,Fcontroversy said via lawyers nothing
OL,9,Finappropriate or unlawful happened
OL,10,Fwith the then-unnamed presenter.
