OL,6,FHe joined the BBC as a trainee in 1984
OL,7,Fand spent four decades with the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster, leading on historic
OL,9,Fevents including the Queen's funeral
OL,10,Fin 2022 and most recently the
OL,11,Fcoronation of the King in May 2023.
OL,13,FHe was the BBC's highest paid
OL,14,Fnewsreader, with a pay bracket of
OL,15,F#435,000`#439,999 in the year 2022/
OL,16,F2023, according to the corporation's
OL,17,Fmost recent annual report.
